<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  Nexa Dir — Chocolatey 패키지(3번째 배포 채널, docs/21-distribution.md §7).
  설계: nupkg는 바이너리를 동봉하지 않고 GitHub Release의 설치형 exe를 내려받아 설치한다
        (PolyForm NC = 비-FOSS → 커뮤니티 저장소 재배포 규정상 공식 URL 다운로드가 정석).
  버전/체크섬은 release.yml이 태그 빌드 시점에 주입한다 — 수동 편집 금지.
-->
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2015/06/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>nexa-dir</id>
    <version>0.0.0</version>
    <packageSourceUrl>https://github.com/SosomLab/nexa-dir2/tree/main/packaging/chocolatey</packageSourceUrl>
    <owners>SosomLab</owners>

    <title>Nexa Dir</title>
    <authors>SosomLab</authors>
    <projectUrl>https://sosomlab.com/apps/nexa-dir/</projectUrl>
    <iconUrl>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/SosomLab/nexa-dir2@0.8.0/crates/nexa-app/assets/nexa-dir-1024.png</iconUrl>
    <copyright>Copyright (c) 2026 SosomLab</copyright>
    <licenseUrl>https://github.com/SosomLab/nexa-dir2/blob/main/LICENSE.md</licenseUrl>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>true</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <projectSourceUrl>https://github.com/SosomLab/nexa-dir2</projectSourceUrl>
    <docsUrl>https://github.com/SosomLab/nexa-dir2/tree/main/docs</docsUrl>
    <bugTrackerUrl>https://github.com/SosomLab/nexa-dir2/issues</bugTrackerUrl>
    <tags>nexa-dir file-manager explorer windows rust portable admin</tags>
    <summary>Lightweight, keyboard-first file explorer for Windows — a single native exe.</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
**Nexa Dir** is a lightweight file explorer for Windows, built as a single native
executable in pure Rust on the Win32 API — no managed runtime, no UI framework,
no external DLLs beyond the OS inbox set.

### Highlights

* **Single portable exe** — under 10 MB, idle memory footprint under 30 MB.
* **Dense, dark, keyboard-first UI** — designed for fast navigation over the mouse.
* **Virtualized tree/list** — smooth over 100k+ entries.
* **Bulk rename** with reusable presets, built-in preview, dual-language UI (English/Korean).

### Notes

* This package installs the machine-wide (all users) build via the official
  installer downloaded from the project's GitHub Releases.
* Settings and session data live next to the exe under `data\`, falling back to
  `%LOCALAPPDATA%\NexaDir2\data` when the install directory is not writable.
  **Uninstalling keeps your data** so a reinstall restores your settings.

### License

Nexa Dir is released under the **PolyForm Noncommercial License 1.0.0** — free for
personal and other noncommercial use. **Commercial use requires a separate paid
license**: kiros33@sosomlab.com / https://sosomlab.com

Product home: https://sosomlab.com/apps/nexa-dir/
]]></description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/SosomLab/nexa-dir2/releases</releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <file src="tools\**" target="tools" />
  </files>
</package>
